`8Keywords``   : Penalty
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * penalty <argument>

 Penalty is a command used for reading and writing penalty notes.  For more
information, see Note Boards. 

 If you're looking for specific penalties for various offenses, try Standard
Penalties.

